<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transcript Application</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="transcript.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="script.js/script.js"></script>
    <style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        height: 70vh;
    }

    .transcript-container {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        margin-top: 80px;
        margin-bottom: 70px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
        flex-direction: column;
    
    }
    .footer-bottom{
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .page-title {
        margin: 20px;
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .transcript-info-card {
        border: none;
        padding: 20px 50px;
        box-shadow: 2px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 15px;
        border-left: 5px solid blue;
        background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .notice-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: black;
    }

    .notice-description {
        font-size: 17px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .disclaimer-box {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 17px;
        background-color: #f8d7da;
        border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
        padding: 7px 12px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .disclaimer-box strong {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #721c24;
    }

    .application-instructions {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .download-section {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .download-link {
        font-size: 19px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: black;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .download-button {
        border: none;
        background-color: #6366f1;;
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 8px 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .download-button a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
    }

    .apply-section {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .apply-button {
        padding: 15px 30px;   
 border-radius: 50px;
 font-size: 1rem;
 font-weight: 600;
 cursor: pointer;
 transition: all 0.3s ease;
 text-decoration: none;
 display: inline-block;
 text-align: center;
 background: #6366f1;
 color: white;
 border: none;
    }

    .apply-button a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .apply-button:hover{
 background: #5855eb;
 transform: translateY(-2px);
}
/* Mobile Responsive Design for Transcript Info Page */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .transcript-container {
    padding: 15px;
  }

  .transcript-info-card {
    padding: 15px 40px;
  }

  .notice-title {
    font-size: 19px;
  }

  .notice-description {
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box {
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box strong {
    font-size: 19px;
  }

  .download-link {
    font-size: 18px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  body {
    height: auto;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .transcript-container {
    padding: 10px;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .transcript-info-card {
    padding: 15px 25px;
    margin: 0 10px;
  }

  .notice-title {
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .notice-description {
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box {
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box strong {
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .application-instructions {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .download-section {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .download-link {
    font-size: 17px;
  }

  .download-button {
    padding: 6px 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .apply-section {
    margin-top: 25px;
  }

  .apply-button {
    padding: 12px 25px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .apply-button a {
    font-size: 18px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .transcript-container {
    padding: 8px;
  }

  .transcript-info-card {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    margin: 0 5px;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .notice-title {
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .notice-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box {
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 5px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box strong {
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .application-instructions {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .download-section {
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .download-link {
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .download-button {
    padding: 5px 7px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .apply-section {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .apply-button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    display: block;
    max-width: 200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .apply-button a {
    font-size: 16px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 360px) {
  .transcript-container {
    padding: 10px 15px;
  }

  .transcript-info-card {
    padding: 10px 15px;
  }

  .notice-title {
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .notice-description {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .disclaimer-box strong {
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .application-instructions {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .download-link {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .apply-button a {
    font-size: 15px;
  }
}

</style>

</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/nav.ejs") %>
    <div class="container transcript-container">
        <div>
            <h1 class="page-title">Transcripts</h1>

            <div class="transcript-info-card">
                <p class="notice-title">
                    Important Notice
                </p>
                <p class="notice-description">
                    To apply for your Transcript, you will need to do the following:
                </p>

                <div class="disclaimer-box">
                    <strong>Disclaimer :</strong> Oduduwa University Academic affairs processes and produces ALL academic transcripts. The office may require up to 30 WORKING days to get your transcript produced. If you need your transcript urgently, please contact Oduduwa University Academic affairs directly. For applications that are not urgent, we are happy to proceed to submit and follow-up on your application. We aim to get your transcript delivered to the requesting organisation between 14 and 30 WORKING days.
                </div>

                <ul class="application-instructions">
                    <li>
                        Complete the Academic affairs form (download it using the link/button below), and attach it to your online application:
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>NOTE:</strong> You can apply for your <strong>unofficial transcript</strong> by sending a mail directly to oduduwauniversity.edu.ng, as the secretariat does not facilitate this service.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <div class="download-section">
                    <a class="download-link" href="./transcript//TRANSCRIPT-REQUEST-FORM (2).docx" download>Transcript Form</a>
                    <button id="downloadBtn" class="download-button">
                        <a href="./transcript/TRANSCRIPT-REQUEST-FORM (2).docx">Download</a>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="apply-section">
                  <a href="/apply-transcript" class="apply-button">Click here to apply</a>
                  
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

      <!-- <footer>
          <div class="footer-bottom">
              <p style="font-size: 20px;">&copy; 2025 OUIAA. All rights reserved.</p>
          </div>
      </footer>   -->
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
          <p>&copy; 2025 OUIAA. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>

      
</body>
</html>
